ustria Musicale Italiana|FIMI]]: Gold<ref>{{cite certification|region=Italy|artist=Hozier|accessdate=21 March 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Music Canada|MC]]: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"MC\">{{cite certification|region=Canada|artist=Hozier|accessdate=21 March 2019}}</ref>\n* [[NVPI]]: Platinum<ref name=\"NVPI\">{{cite web|url=https://nvpi.nl/nvpi-audio/marktinformatie/goud-platina/|title=Goud/Platina \u2013 NVPI Audio|format=To access, enter the search parameter \"Hozier\" and select \"Search\"|accessdate=6 September 2018|publisher=[[NVPI]]|language=Dutch}}</ref>\n* [[Recording Industry Association of America|RIAA]]: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\">{{cite web | url=https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&se=Hozier#search_section | title=American certifications \u2013 Hozier| publisher=[[Recording Industry Association of America]] | accessdate=1 February 2016}}</ref>\n* [[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]]: Gold<ref>{{cite certification|region=New Zealand|type=album|artist=Hozier|title=Hozier|recent=website|id=4099|accessdate=17 July 2015}}</ref>\n|\n* WW: 1,000,000<ref name=\"IRE-cert\"/>\n*[[Irish Recorded Music Association|IRE]]: 7,300 (1st week)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/irelands-fastest-selling-debut-albums-of-the-decade-between-2010-2019__27513/|title=Ireland's fastest-selling debut albums of the decade|website=www.officialcharts.com|language=en|access-date=2019-11-23}}</ref>\n* [[Nielsen SoundScan|US]]: 972,000<ref name=\"WB BB200\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Wasteland, Baby!]]''\n|\n*Release: 1 March 2019<ref name=\"wasteland\">{{cite web|url=http://ventsmagazine.com/2018/12/10/hozier-announces-spring-north-american-headline-tour-in-support-of-forthcoming-sophomore-album-wasteland-baby/|title=Hozier announces Spring North American headline tour in support of forthcoming sophomore album Wasteland, Baby|date=10 December 2018|work=Vents Magazine|accessdate=12 December 2018}}</ref>\n* Label: Rubyworks, Island\n* Format: CD, 