um\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Irish Singles Chart|IRE]]<br/><ref name=\"IRE\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://australian-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Hozier|title=australian-charts.com - Discography Hozier|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=4 April 2015}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Ultratop|BEL<br>(FL)]]<br/><ref name=\"FL\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Canadian Hot 100|CAN]]<br/><ref name=\"CANSongs\">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/6059764/hozier/chart?f=793|title=Hozier \u2013 Chart History: Billboard Canadian Hot 100|publisher=[[Prometheus Global Media]]|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[GfK Entertainment|GER]]<br/><ref name=\"GER\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|ITA]]<br/><ref name=\"ITA\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Single Top 100|NLD]]<br/><ref name=\"NL\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ]]<br/><ref name=\"NZ\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br/><ref name=\"UK\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Billboard Hot 100|US]]<br/><ref name=\"US100\">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/music/hozier/chart-history/hot-100|title=Hozier Chart History: The Hot 100|work=Billboard|accessdate=17 September 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Take Me to Church]]\"\n| 2013\n| 2 || 2 || 1 || 2 || 2 || 1 || 2 || 2 || 2 || 2\n|\n* [[Australian Recording Industry Association|ARIA]]: 8\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"ARIA-2019\">{{cite web|url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.aupagesSinglesAccreds2019.htm|title=ARIA Charts \u2013 Accreditations \u2013 2019 Singles.|publisher=[[Australian Recor