y: Billboard 200|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=17 September 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Hozier (album)|Hozier]]''\n| \n* Release: 19 September 2014\n* Label: [[Rubyworks Records|Rubyworks]], [[Island Records|Island]]\n* Format: [[Compact disc|CD]], [[LP record|LP]], [[Music download|digital download]]\n| 1 || 3 || 2 || 2 || 14 || 7 || 7 || 3 || 3 || 2\n| \n* [[Irish Recorded Music Association|IRMA]]: 6\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"IRE-cert\">{{cite journal|url=http://www.rte.ie/ten/news/2015/0410/693231-hozier-returns-to-irish-number-one-spot/|title=Hozier dethrones James Bay to reclaim Irish No 1|journal=RT\u00c9 News|date=10 April 2015|accessdate=28 April 2015}}</ref>\n* [[Australian Recording Industry Association|ARIA]]: Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.noise11.com/news/aria-albums-triple-js-like-a-version-11-stops-cold-chisel-from-debuting-at-no-1-20151010|title=ARIA Albums: Triple J's 'Like a Version 11' Stops Cold Chisel From Debuting At No 1|publisher=Noise11|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|date=10 October 2015|accessdate=10 October 2015}}</ref>\n* [[British Phonographic Industry|BPI]]: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bpi.co.uk/brit-certified/|title=Certified Awards Search|publisher=[[British Phonographic Industry]]|accessdate=4 October 2019|format=To access, enter the search parameter \"Hozier\" and select \"Search by Keyword\"}}</ref>\n* [[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|FIMI]]: Gold<ref>{{cite certification|region=Italy|artist=Hozier|accessdate=21 March 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Music Canada|MC]]: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"MC\">{{cite certification|region=Canada|artist=Hozier|accessdate=21 March 2019}}</ref>\n* [[NVPI]]: Platinum<ref name=\"NVPI\">{{cite web|url=https://nvpi.nl/nvpi-audio/marktinformatie/goud-platina/|title=Goud/Platina \u2013 NVPI Audio|format=To access, enter the search parameter \"Hozier\" and select \"Search\"|accessdate=6 September 2018|publisher=[[NVPI]]|language=Dutch}}</ref>\n* [[Recording Industry Association of America|RIAA]]: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\">{{cite web | url=https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&se=Hozier#search_section | title=American certifications \u2013 Hozier| publisher=[[Recording Industry Association of America]] | accessdate=1 February 2016}}</ref>\n* [[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]]: Gold<ref>{{cite certification|region=New Zealand|type=album|artist=Hozier|title=Hozier|recent=website|id=4099|accessdate=17 July 2015}}</ref>\n|\n* WW: 1,000,000<ref name=\"IRE-cert\"/>\n*[[Irish Recorded Music Association|IRE]]: 7,300 (1st week)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/irelands-fastest-selling-debut-albums-of-the-decade-between-2010-2019__27513/|title=Ireland's fastest-selling debut albums of the decade|website=www.officialcharts.com|language=en|access-date=2019-11-23}}</ref>\n* [[Nielsen SoundScan|US]]: 972,000<ref name=\"WB BB200\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Wasteland, Baby!]]''\n|\n*Release: 1 March 2019<ref name=\"wasteland\">{{cite web|url=http://ventsmagazine.com/2018/12/10/hozier-announces-spring-north-american-headline-tour-in-support-of-forthcoming-sophomore-album-wasteland-baby/|title=Hozier announces Spring North American headline tour in support of forthcoming sophomore album Wasteland, Baby|date=10 December 2018|work=Vents Magazine|accessdate=12 December 2018}}</ref>\n* Label: Rubyworks, Island\n* Format: CD, LP, digital download\n| 1 || 8 || 19 || 9 || 15 || \u2014 || 17 || 9 || 6 || 1\n|\n|\n* US: 75,000<ref name=\"WB BB200\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8501829/hozier-debuts-no-1-billboard-200-chart-wasteland-baby|title=Hozier Debuts at No. 1 on Billboard 200 Albums Chart With 'Wasteland, Baby!'|work=Billboard|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|date=10 March 2019|accessdate=11 March 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Extended plays===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"