y/bubbling-under-hot-100|title=Hozier Chart History \u2013 Bubbling Under Hot 100|work=Billboard|accessdate=27 November 2018}}</ref>}}\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Someone New (Hozier song)|Someone New]]\"\n| 13 || 24 || \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Someone New\" did not enter the Flanders Ultratop 50, but peaked at number 5 on the Ultratip chart.<ref name=\"FL\"/>}} || 90 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Someone New\" did not enter the Netherlands' Single Top 100 but peaked on the Netherlands' Single Tip Chart at number 10.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dutchcharts.nl/weekchart.asp?cat=st&year=2015&date=20150718|title=Netherlands Single Tip Chart - 18/07/2015|publisher=[[Mega Charts]]|date=July 18, 2015|accessdate=May 22, 2019}}</ref>}} || 13 || 19 || \u2014{{efn-ua|\"Someone New\" did not enter the Billboard Hot 100, but peaked at number one on the Bubbling Under Hot 100 chart.<ref name=\"Bubbling Under Hot 100\"/>}}\n|\n* ARIA: Platinum<ref name=\"ARIA-2019\"/>\n* BPI: Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* FIMI: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fimi.it/certificazioni#/category:singoli/year:2019/page:1|title=Hozier - Someone New|website=Fimi.it|language=it|accessdate=7 January 2019}}</ref>\n* RMNZ: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=4085|title=NZ Top 40 Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|accessdate=26 June 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Jackie & Wilson\"{{citation needed|date=January 2019}}\n| 68 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Jackie & Wilson\" did not enter the ''Billboard'' Canadian Hot 100, but peaked at number 64 on the [[Canadian Digital Song Sales]] chart.<ref name=\"Canada-digital\">{{cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/music/hozier/chart-history/hot-canada-digital-song-sales |title=Hozier: Hot Canadian Digital Songs |work=Billboard |accessdate=22 May 2019}}</ref>}} || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 \n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Cherry Wine 